Topped with red chili, fresh cottage cheese, lemon juice, and fresh coriander leaves. Accompaniments- Green dip and bhuyjiya mix. Allergens: Dairy and nuts

info.description: Protein-enriched poha has well-soaked organic poha tossed with cumin, mustard seeds, green chili, ginger, onion, tomato, peas, green beans, soya, chili flakes, and oregano. Topped with peanuts, red chili, and lemon. Accompaniments- Green dip and murukku. Allergens: Soya

info.name: Shredded Chicken Cold Sandwich
info.description: Shredded chicken, multigrain bread, iceberg lettuce, tomato, onion, And drizzle with low-fat homemade sauces.

info.name: Daily Diet Sprout Salad
info.description: Vibrant sprout salad with crisp iceberg lettuce, red onion, tomatoes, green capsicum, and red cabbage. Garnished with pomegranate seeds and parsley leaves, and served with a lemon wedge and seven-herb olive lime dressing.

info.name: Classic Chicken Salad
info.description: Refreshing salad featuring assorted lettuce, cucumber, chicken, eggs, green beans, cherry tomatoes, olives, and red onions, served with a mustard yoghurt and lemon slice.

info.name: Nutty Chicken Salad
info.description: Nutty chicken salad with assorted lettuce, topped with tossed chicken. Includes crunchy carrot, sweet corn, gherkins, orange, cherry tomatoes, red cabbage, sour cheese, black olives, and roasted peanuts, served with sweet chili yoghurt.

info.name: Avocado Teriyaki Glazed Chicken Salad
info.description: Vibrant salad featuring teriyaki-tossed chicken, assorted lettuce, cabbage, colorful capsicum, cucumber, avocado, pineapple, broccoli, cherry tomatoes, jalapenos, black olives, carrots, sesame seeds, and spring onions. Served with crushed chili-lime yoghurt.

info.name: Southwest BBQ Grilled Chicken Salad
info.description: Refreshing BBQ salad featuring a base of assorted lettuce, topped with barbecue-style tossed chicken, corn, and mushrooms. Enhanced by vibrant red, yellow, and green capsicum, red onion, cucumber, broccoli, black olives, cherry tomatoes, and jalapenos. Served with spicy jalapeno yoghurt.

info.name: Chicken Caesar Salad
info.description: Colorful salad featuring tossed chicken, assorted lettuce, red cabbage, green, yellow, and red capsicum, cherry tomatoes, red onion, black olives, Parmesan, and parsley. Served with house Caesar yoghurt and homemade croutons.

info.name: Smoked Paprika Chicken Salad
info.description: Refreshing salad of assorted lettuce, topped with tossed chicken. Enhanced with colorful capsicum, cabbage, red onion, jalapenos, black olives, cherry tomatoes, roasted sumac peanuts, and parsley. Served with spicy jalapeno yoghurt and lemon slice.

info.name: Roasted Chicken Salad
info.description: Fresh salad with assorted lettuce, topped with roast chicken, colorful capsicum, cucumber, cherry tomatoes, red onion, red cabbage, black olives, and jalapenos. Garnished with parsley and served with ranch yoghurt.

info.name: Cocktail Fruit Crunch Salad
info.description: Colorful fruit salad with assorted lettuce, complemented by sun melon, red apple, pineapple, cranberries, grapes, kiwi, and blueberries. Garnished with walnuts, pomegranate, golden raisins, cottage cheese, mint, and pumpkin seeds. Served with fruity Greek yoghurt.

info.name: BBQ Cottage Cheese Salad
info.description: Vibrant BBQ salad with assorted lettuce, topped with barbecue-tossed cottage cheese, corn, and mushrooms. Includes red, yellow, and green capsicum, red onion, cucumber, broccoli, olives, cherry tomatoes, and jalapenos. Served with spicy jalapeno yoghurt.

info.name: Gourmet Veg Caesar Salad
info.description: Fresh Caesar salad with tossed cottage cheese, iceberg, assorted lettuce, colorful capsicum, red cabbage, cherry tomatoes, red onion, and black olives. Finished with Parmesan, parsley, And served house Caesar yoghurt, and homemade croutons.

info.name: Teriyaki Tofu Nutty Salad
info.description: Colorful salad with assorted lettuce, topped with tossed tofu. Includes crunchy orange carrot, sweet corn, gherkins, orange segments, cherry tomatoes, red cabbage, black olives, roasted peanuts, and fresh mint, served with sweet chili yoghurt.

info.name: Pan Tossed Cottage Cheese Salad
info.description: Vibrant salad with assorted lettuce, topped with tossed cottage cheese. Includes green, yellow, and red capsicum, cucumber, broccoli, red cabbage, baby corn, black olives, cherry tomatoes, jalapenos, and red onion, served with garlic chili yoghurt.

info.name: One Pot BBQ Chicken Spaghetti
info.description: Zucchini, bell peppers, onion, mushrooms, broccoli, and BBQ chicken mixed well with creamy chipotle sauce. Topped with cherry tomato, black olives, jalapenos, and parsley.

info.name: Hand Crushed Garlic Pesto Spaghetti
info.description: Scrumptious spaghetti combines tossed bell peppers, capsicum, zucchini, onion, mushroom, and pesto with exotic herbs. Topped with cherry tomato, olives, jalapenos, broccoli, and basil. Allergens: Wheat and dairy

info.name: Creamy Pesto Chicken Parmesan
info.description: Pasta loaded with exotic veggies, colorful capsicum, mushroom, baby corn, sauteed onion and chicken. Garnished with cherry tomato, black olives, basil leaves and parmesan. "

info.name: Sundried Tomato Chipotle Olive Spaghetti

info.name: Creamy Pesto Basil Parmesan
info.description: Pasta is tossed in a creamy pesto sauce, mix bell peppers, mushrooms, baby corn, and red onion. Topped with cherry tomato, black olive, fresh basil leaves, and parmesan cheese.

info.name: Chipotle Sauteed Vegetable Pasta

info.name: Teriyaki Chicken Rice Bowl
info.description: (Serves 1) Tender chicken pieces stir-fried with assorted vegetables(carrot, red cabbage, baby corn, mushroom, broccoli) over some fragrant basmati rice, and a blend of savory sauces. Topped with fried nuts, steamed egg, sliced jalapenos, red paprika, and spring onion, this bowl delivers an irresistible fusion of sweet, spicy, and umami flavors.

info.name: Grilled Chicken Rice Bowl
info.description: (Serves 1) A hearty and nutritious bowl featuring tender grilled chicken tossed with a medley of vegetables(corn, black beans, carrot, baby corn, mushroom, broccoli), served over a bed of aromatic rice and garnished with fresh hummus, crisp pita, and a zesty olive tapenade. This bowl is a perfect balance of protein, fiber, and vibrant flavors.

info.name: Falafel Hummus Power Bowl
info.description: (Serves 1) (vegan) A delightful Middle Eastern-inspired bowl featuring crispy falafel and creamy hummus served over a bed of fluffy rice. Accompanied by fresh vegetables(corn, black beans, carrot, baby corn, mushroom, broccoli), crisp pita, olive tapenade, fresh pomegranate seeds, and parsley, perfect for a satisfying and wholesome meal.

info.name: Chicken Tikka Rice Bowl
info.description: (Serves 1) Succulent pieces of marinated chicken tikka and sauteed vegetables(onion, capsicum, zucchini) served over a bed of aromatic basmati rice, garnished with chickpea salad, olives, fresh mint & almond flakes. This bowl offers a delightful blend of flavors and textures that will transport your taste buds to the heart of India.

info.name: Vegan Thai Tofu Rice Bowl
info.description: (Serves 1) (vegan) A vegetarian twist on the Indonesian classic. Fluffy basmati rice with tofu, fresh vegetables(carrot, red cabbage, baby corn, mushroom, broccoli), and a fragrant blend of sauces. Topped with crisp fried nuts, sliced jalapenos and red paprika, this bowl offers a delightful balance of sweet, spicy, and savory flavors.

info.name: Barbecue Paneer Rice Bowl
info.description: (Serves 1) Tandoori marinated paneer cubes paired with fresh vegetables(onion, capsicum, zucchini), served over fragrant basmati rice. Garnished with chickpea salad, olives, fresh mint & almond flakes, this bowl offers a vibrant and satisfying vegetarian option with a blend of rich, savory flavors.

info.name: Tropical Fruit Juice

info.name: Watermelon Juice
info.description: Refresh your hot summer day with the chilled juice made out of watermelon, lemon and ice cubes.

info.name: Daily Green Juice
info.description: Goodness of greens and essential vegetables in a juice. Choose your variant from the choices!

info.name: Hummus With Pita Triangles
info.description: The Mediterranean specialty is creamier hummus topped with jalapenos, cherry tomato, pomegranate, parsley and black olive served with freshly baked pita bread. Allergen: Wheat

info.name: Ultimate Pan Chicken Nachos
info.description: All more the reason to enjoy for chicken lovers. Nachos combined with chunks of pan tossed chicken and homemade salsa making it a delightful and innovative salad to die for. When stomach craves for hunger, this will surely give a treat to you taste buds.

info.name: Double Cheese Bean Nachos
info.description: One must not wait for what this cheesy blast has to offer. A nutritional salad with crunchy nachos combined with double cheese and bean. A snack to munch on at any time of the day.

info.name: Khatti Meethi Basil Bhelpuri
info.description: Our take on the innovative bhelpuri with crispy puffed rice, roasted mung, cornflakes, dried fruit raisins, cashew nuts, peanuts, healthy seeds, and basil. Accompanied by red chopped onion, tomato, green chilies, pomegranate, lemon, and coriander. Served with green spicy dip and red sweet dip.

info.name: Fruit Lime Exotic Bowl Salad
info.description: Refreshing fruit salad featuring juicy sun melon, crisp red apple, pineapple, cranberries, red grapes, orange slices, kiwi, and blueberries. Garnished with walnuts, pomegranate seeds, cottage cheese cubes, and fresh mint leaves, served with a tangy strawberry lime dressing for a vibrant finish. "

info.name: Vrat Bhog Sabudana Khichdi
info.description: Vrat special curated sabudana khichdi is freshly prepared with rock salt for your fasting. Well soaked sabudana is combined with healthy vrat friendly oil and seasoning  & tossed with finely chopped ginger, green chili, diced boiled potato, Topped with crushed groundnuts, pomegranate seeds, raisins, fresh paneer cubes and coriander leaves as garnishes, served with green chutney and vrat peanuts.  Note: Made with sendha namak, no onion, no garlic, less spicy, and less oil.

info.name: Vrat Special Sabudana Khichdi
info.description: Sabudana tossed with vrat friendly veggies, Indian herbs tempering, rock salt , vrat friendly oil and seasoning,  Topped with coconut, coriander, pomegranate. seved with green spicy dip and vrat special peanuts. Note: Made with sendha namak, no onion, no garlic, less spicy, and less oil.

info.name: Roasted Garlic Chicken Tomato Soup
info.description: Warm and pleasant chicken soup combines tomato with spring onion, basil, garlic, and juicy well-done chicken with parsley. Hint of black pepper. Accompaniments - soup sticks, butter and seasoning. Allergen: NA

info.name: Basil Sundried Tomato Soup
info.description: Fulfilling and smooth in texture soup has tomatoes with spring onion, basil, and garlic with parsley. Hint of black pepper. Accompaniments - soup sticks, butter and seasoning. Allergen: NA

info.name: Ground Nuts Sabudana Khichdi
info.description: Classic sabudana khichdi is a combination of well-soaked sabudana, tossed with cumin, mustard seeds, fresh curry leaves, green chili, ginger, tomato, capsicum, chili flakes, and oregano. Topped with peanuts, pomegranate, beetroot, fresh cottage cheese and fresh coriander leaves as garnishing. Accompaniments- Green dip and peanuts. Allergens: Dairy and nuts

info.name: Nutty Pineapple Sabudana Khichdi
info.description: Pineapple-flavored twist and scrumptious sabudana khichdi is a combination of well-soaked sabudana tossed with cumin, mustard seeds, curry leaves, green chili, ginger, tomato, bell peppers, capsicum, fresh pineapple, broccoli, chili flakes, and oregano. Topped with peanuts and fresh coriander leaves. Accompaniments- Green dip and peanuts. Allergen: Nuts

info.name: Oatmeal Cookies
info.description: Leaning towards the healthier side these oatmeal cookies have an incredibly crisp crunchy and chewy texture.  [ pack of 2pc ]
